snippet.title: Super Alloy Ranger Enter the Dragon Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1944060/Super_Alloy_Ranger

Super Alloy Ranger is a 2D side-scrolling action game. Play as Marksman Kelly or Combat Robot No.2 to challenge different levels within the dangerous Machine Empire and unlock new weapons. Use Kelly’s shooting and No.2’s deathblows to defeat abnormal Machine Bosses!
